sentences: Niño del Mar C. Volante (born January 25, 1978), better known as Nyoy Volante, is a Filipino acoustic pop singer-songwriter and actor.
Niño del Mar C. Volante (born January 25, 1978), better known as Nyoy Volante, is a Filipino acoustic pop singer-songwriter and actor.
He was a Tawag Ng Tanghalan Kids hurado, and is currently one of the Tawag Ng Tanghalan hurados.
Volante was born on January 25, 1978 to parents Oliver Volante and Evangeline C. Volante.
Volante started his career at the early 2000s.
In 2015, he was one of the eight contestants of the first season of Your Face Sounds Familiar.
In 2015, he made his acting debut on ABS-CBN on the TV series Ningning.
He played Lola, the title character in Atlantis Productions Kinky Boots in 2018 and 2019 in Carlos P. Romulo Auditorium, Makati.
Spirits: Reawaken as Maestro Jose Carpio (iWant, 2018)
Volante had a relationship with fellow Filipino singer Nina but their relationship ended in 2007.
In 2009, she sued Volante's parents allegedly with estafa case after they failed to settle their 1.4-million peso debt.
On February 24, 2016, he got married with Filipino theater actress Mikkie Bradshaw at the Manila Cathedral, Intramuros, Manila, Philippines.
